snippet.title: Preppie! II for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Preppie! II is the sequel to Preppie!. Howevwer, unlike Preppie!, Preppie! II is not a Frogger clone. Instead you have to paint the grounds of the levels with a certain color, while avoiding frogs, lawnmowers and various vehicles.


What I think:
